hose names are far less known. At the end of the complex, exciting, and at times dismaying chronicle, it is likely that readers will never again watch Hollywood films without thinking about the roles of makeup and hairdressing in creating both fictional characters and stars as emblems of an idealized and undeniably mesmerizing visual perfection.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aBeauty operatorszCaliforniazLos AngelesvBiography. 0aFilm hairstyling. 0aFilm makeup. 0aMakeup artistszCaliforniazLos AngelesvBiography. 0aMotion picturesxProduction and directionzCaliforniazLos AngelesxHistoryy20th century. 0aMotion pictureszCaliforniazLos AngelesxHistory. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh  abeauty, makeup, beauty standards, hair, hairdressing, Hollywood, film, television, T.V., fame, celebrity, cosmetics, makeup artists, hairdresser, gender, silent film, media, studio, studio era, studio film era, cosmetology, history, flawless, image.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2022z9783110992809oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2022 Englishz978311099281608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertRutgers University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076647940uhttps://doi.org/10.36019/9780813563602?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780813563602423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780813563602/original  a978-3-11-076647-9  Rutgers University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099281-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Des